        <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:41:55 +0000</pubDate>
        <guid>/news/2025/gaiasky_3.6.5/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;游닉 Today, coinciding with the end of the sky-scanning phase of Gaia, we publish GaiaSky 3.6.5. The most noteworthy addition is the introduction of the volume rendering infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;fig-center fig-post&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;/img/2025/01/3.6.5-release.jpg&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;decoding=&#34;async&#34; /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/picture&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;            &lt;h4&gt;Gaia Sky 3.6.5 welcome screen.&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;</description>
      </item> 
